The '''Fras''' were a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] tigers who were aggressive but luxury-loving. They generally spent most of their [[Time/Legends|time]] [[Sleep/Legends|asleep]] or lazing about, only being active for about three or four [[Standard hour/Legends|hours]] a [[Standard day/Legends|day]] although they generally spent this time being very active. In fights, they were very aggressive and were liable to [[Diet/Legends|eat]] fallen foes.

